Business
Cedar Creek is a leading wholesale building materials distribution company that began as one yard in Tulsa, OK, in 1977. The company has since expanded its operations to more than 30 distribution facilities and today provides services in 29 states across the Midwest and Southeast. It is one of the country’s premier cedar distributors and largest lumber and manufactured wood distributors.
Charlesbank Investment
We teamed with former portfolio company executive Bill Adams to explore platform acquisitions in the building products sector. In 2010, our year-long effort culminated in a partnership with management to recapitalize Cedar Creek, a wholesale lumber distributor, with Charlesbank acquiring a majority stake. 
